  {id: 10, title_es: "Ayuda", title_eu: "Laguntza", body_es: "<div class=\"video\"><object data=\"https://www.irekia.euskadi.net/video/flowplayer-3.2.15.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"610\" height=\"350\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.irekia.euskadi.net/video/flowplayer-3.2.15.swf\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><param name=\"flashvars\" value=\"config={&quot;key&quot;:&quot;#$61de7613ee9761041ce&quot;,    &quot;playlist&quot;:[&quot;http://bideoak2.euskadi.net//paginas/ayuda_acercade/nueva_home_irekia.jpg&quot;, {&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http://bideoak2.euskadi.net/paginas/ayuda_acercade/nueva_home_irekia_es.flv?emb=1&quot;,&quot;autoPlay&quot;:false,&quot;provider&quot;:&quot;lighttpd&quot;}],    &quot;canvas&quot;:{&quot;backgroundColor&quot;:&quot;#1180B8&quot;},    &quot;plugins&quot;:{&quot;lighttpd&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http://www.irekia.euskadi.net/video/flowplayer.pseudostreaming-3.2.11.swf&quot;},&quot;gatracker&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http://www.irekia.euskadi.net/video/flowplayer.analytics-3.2.8.swf&quot;,&quot;accountId&quot;: &quot;UA-10951282-1&quot;}}}\" /></object></div>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>En el siguiente video se muestra el funcionamiento de <strong>IREKIA</strong> y las diferentes herramientas que existen para hacer llegar al Gobierno Vasco comentarios, aportaciones, modificaciones o sugerencias.</p>\r\n<p>Es un recorrido r&aacute;pido, de apenas unos minutos, que os animamos a realizar si no hab&eacute;is navegado antes por <strong>IREKIA</strong>.</p>\r\n<p>Buen viaje!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>", body_eu: "<p><object data=\"https://www.irekia.euskadi.net/video/flowplayer-3.2.15.swf\" type=\"application/x-shockwave-flash\" width=\"610\" height=\"350\"><param name=\"movie\" value=\"http://www.irekia.euskadi.net/video/flowplayer-3.2.15.swf\" /><param name=\"allowfullscreen\" value=\"true\" /><param name=\"allowscriptaccess\" value=\"always\" /><param name=\"flashvars\" value=\"config={&quot;key&quot;:&quot;#$61de7613ee9761041ce&quot;,    &quot;playlist&quot;:[&quot;http://bideoak2.euskadi.net//paginas/ayuda_acercade/nueva_home_irekia.jpg&quot;, {&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http://bideoak2.euskadi.net/paginas/ayuda_acercade/nueva_home_irekia_es.flv?emb=1&quot;,&quot;autoPlay&quot;:false,&quot;provider&quot;:&quot;lighttpd&quot;}],    &quot;canvas&quot;:{&quot;backgroundColor&quot;:&quot;#1180B8&quot;},    &quot;plugins&quot;:{&quot;lighttpd&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http://www.irekia.euskadi.net/video/flowplayer.pseudostreaming-3.2.11.swf&quot;},&quot;gatracker&quot;:{&quot;url&quot;:&quot;http://www.irekia.euskadi.net/video/flowplayer.analytics-3.2.8.swf&quot;,&quot;accountId&quot;: &quot;UA-10951282-1&quot;}}}\" /></object></p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>\r\n<p>Ondoko bideoan IREKIAren funtzionamendua azaltzen da, baita Eusko Jaurlaritzari iruzkinak, ekarpenak, aldaketak edo iradokizunak helarazteko dauden tresnak ere.</p>\r\n<p>Ibilbide azkarra da, minutu batzuk besterik ez dira; lehenago IREKIAtik ibili ez bazarete tutorial hau egitera gonbidatzen zaituztegu.</p>\r\n<p>Ondo joan!</p>\r\n<p>&nbsp;</p>", has_comments: false, created_by: nil, updated_by: 1, comments_closed: true, has_comments_with_photos: false, position: 100, has_ratings: false, title_en: nil, body_en: nil, published_at: "2014-07-06 22:00:00", type: "Page", comments_count: 0, starts_at: nil, ends_at: nil, place: nil, speaker_es: nil, lat: nil, lng: nil, location_for_gmaps: nil, organization_id: 1, speaker_eu: nil, speaker_en: nil, cover_photo_file_name: nil, cover_photo_content_type: nil, cover_photo_file_size: nil, cover_photo_updated_at: nil, cover_photo_alt_es: nil, city: nil, has_journalists: nil, has_photographers: nil, streaming_live: false, irekia_coverage: false, irekia_coverage_photo: false, irekia_coverage_video: false, irekia_coverage_audio: false, cover_photo_alt_eu: nil, cover_photo_alt_en: nil, multimedia_dir: "help", multimedia